title: Episode 19 | The Black Album (feat. Young Guru & Hip Hop)
description: Rory & Mal sit down with Hip Hop & Young Guru to celebrate and reflect on the 18th birthday of the Black Album recently passing. The guys run through it song by song, discussing the stories and inspiration behind the iconic album.
author: newrorymal@gmail.com (More Sauce)
